_description: A Lover’s Farewell to his Mistress, perhaps by a Duke of York — thirty-four quatrains

BodDou95.First Lines:
Excellent soueraine semely to seePreved prudence peerlees of
                    pris…
BodDou95.Last Lines:
…How euere y fare ffarewell yeffarewell prymerose my
                    plesaunce
